// EcosystemScale v2.3: Finalized Orbit Cluster Expansion, Button Visual Refinements, and Component Stripping
---

<section class="w-full pt-6 md:pt-10 pb-20 md:pb-28 bg-white select-none relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    
    <!-- SINGLE STAGE UNIFIED LAYOUT -->
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center relative">
      
      <!-- LEFT COMPONENT: Phone Epicenter with Dense Orbiting Cluster -->
      <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center h-[540px] md:h-[640px] order-2 lg:order-1">
         
         <!-- Spatial Glow -->
         <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-gray-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-90 pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

         <!-- THE CENTRAL DEVICE -->
