               Wake Up to a Full Content Calendar. Every Morning.
            </h2>
            
            <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
            <p class="text-[15px] md:text-[16px] text-[#4B5563] font-medium font-geist max-w-xl leading-relaxed mt-1">
               Xeni works overnight—generating visuals, writing captions, and queuing posts while you sleep. In the morning, review fresh drafts in your queue. Approve what you like, tweak the rest. Your content calendar fills itself, weeks ahead.
            </p>
